io.confluent.ksql.engine.generic

Class KsqlGenericRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.confluent.ksql.engine.generic.KsqlGenericRecord

  • public final class KsqlGenericRecord
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a record in ksqlDB which consists of a GenericKey key, a GenericRow value and a long timestamp. This is mostly used when generating data from SQL expressions.
